  - {MapperOrClient} (mapper or external client)
- Methods to cover:
  - {method1Signature}
  - {method2Signature}
  - {method3Signature}

Requirements (use modern JUnit 5 patterns):
- Use JUnit Jupiter (JUnit 5) with:
  - @Nested to group tests by method
  - @DisplayName for readability
  - @ParameterizedTest + @MethodSource for input variations
  - AssertJ assertions (assertThat…)
  - Mockito with @ExtendWith(MockitoExtension.class), @Mock, @InjectMocks
  - Verify interactions (verify / verifyNoMoreInteractions)
  - Include failure-path tests:
    - not found -> ResourceNotFoundException
    - validation -> IllegalArgumentException or BusinessRuleViolationException
- Follow Arrange → Act → Assert and clear naming conventions
- Don’t use SpringBootTest for this (pure unit test only)
- Add helper builders/mothers for DTO/entity test data
- Keep tests deterministic (no random, no time dependency)

Output:
